GOALS: Make bonuses from killing dragons cooler, preserve multiple build options, make abilities more related to the elemental drakes, make flame breath a high damage channel, double down on the fantasy of R with a pantheon ultimate style dragon leap.

[Fury of the Dragonborn]

INNATE - ELEMENTAL ATTONEMENT: Shyvana gains bonuses on her abilities for every elemental dragon slain by her or her team.

1 DRAGON SLAIN - FLOW OF THE OCEAN: Shyvana heals for 0.5 - 5 (based on level) (+ 5% bonus AD) (+ 2.5% AP) health per second per enemy champion affected by embers.

2 DRAGONS SLAIN - BULWARK OF THE MOUNTAINS: Shyvana gains earthen scale plates during dragon form, granting her bonus armor and magic resistance the higher her health is. 40 armor and magic resistance between 100 - 75% health, 30 between 74 - 50% health, 20 between 49 - 25% health, and 10 between 24 - 0% health.

3 DRAGONS SLAIN - SWIFTNESS OF THE CLOUDS: Shyvana can move during Dragon Breath while slowing herself by 40%.

4 DRAGONS SLAIN - FURY OF THE INFERNAL: Flame Breath, Dragon's Descent, and Dragon Breath apply embers for 3 seconds to enemies effected.

5 DRAGONS SLAIN - GIFT OF THE ELDER: Embers deal true damage.


INNATE - DRAGONBORN: Shyvana increases the bonuses she receives from slaying elemental dragons by 40 / 60 / 80 / 100% (At levels 1 / 6 / 11 / 16).

Additionally, Shyvana deals 20% bonus physical damage and magic damage to Dragons.

[Ocean's Bite]
COOLDOWN: 10 / 9 / 8 / 7 / 6

ACTIVE: Shyvana empowers her next basic attack within 6 seconds to gain 25 bonus range, deal 100% AD (+ 35% AP) and cause her to strike again after 0.25 seconds, which deals bonus magic damage, applies on-hit and on-attack effects at 100% effectiveness and heals her, reduced against minions.

BONUS MAGIC DAMAGE:
40 / 45 / 50 / 55 / 60% AD (+ 25% AP) (+ 10% bonus Health)
HEALING AGAINST MINIONS:
2 - 20 (based on level) (+ 4 / 4.5 / 5 / 5.5 / 6% AD) (+ 2.5% AP) (+ 1% bonus Health)
HEALING AGAINST CHAMPIONS:
10 - 100 (based on level) (+ 20 / 22.5 / 25 / 27.5 / 30% AD) (+ 12.5% AP) (+ 5% bonus Health)

The healing is increased by up to 50% based on her missing health, capping out at 30% health.
INCREASED HEALING AGAINST MINIONS:
3 - 30 (based on level) (+ 6 / 6.75 / 7.5 / 8.25 / 9% AD) (+ 3.75% AP) (+ 1.5% bonus Health)
INCREASED HEALING AGAINST CHAMPIONS:
15 - 150 (based on level) (+ 30 / 33.75 / 37.5 / 41.25 / 45) (+ 18.75 AP) (+ 7.5% bonus Health)

Basic attacks reduce Twin Bite's cooldown by 0.5 seconds on-hit.

DRAGON FORM BONUS: Shyvana instantly attacks enemies in a cone around the target before applying Twin Bite's effects to each of them. The basic attacks deal 100% AD (+ 35% AP) physical damage, are affected by critical strike modifiers, and apply on-hit effects to each target hit. The second strike cannot critically strike nor trigger on-attack effects, but it will still apply on-hit effects. Additionally, Twin Bite's empowered attack has an uncancellable windup.

Healing from additional targets is reduced by 20% per additional target, down to 40%.

Shyvana creates a pool of water below each enemy champion hit for 2 seconds, slowing all enemies who pass through the pool. While Fiery Winds flame aura collides with the water pools, steam creates, dealing additional damage over time to enemies who remain in the steam.  

SLOW:
20  / 30 / 40% (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)
MAGIC DAMAGE PER TICK:
0.5 - 15 (based on level) (+ 2.5 / 5 / 7.5 (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)) (+ 2.5% bonus AD) (+ 1.25% AP) (+ 0.5% bonus Health)

Twin Bite resets Shyvana's basic attack timer.

[Fiery Winds]
COOLDOWN: 16 / 15 / 14 / 13 / 12

PASSIVE: Shyvana creates a flame aura around herself, dealing magic damage each 0.5 seconds to nearby enemies and marking enemies hit with embers for 3 seconds.

MAGIC DAMAGE PER TICK:
1 - 30 (based on level) (+ 5 / 7.5 / 10 / 12.5 / 15) (+ 5% bonus AD) (+ 2.5% AP) (+ 1% bonus Health)

Enemies marked with embers take additional magic damage over 3 seconds based on their maximum health, Shyvana's basic attacks deal a portion of this damage on hit.

MAGIC DAMAGE OVER TIME:
2 - 6% (based on level) (+ 1 / 1.25 / 1.5 / 1.75 / 2%) (+ 2% per 100 bonus AD) (+ 1% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health

MAGIC DAMAGE ON HIT:
1 - 3% (based on level) (+ 0.5 / 0.625 / 0.75 / 0.875 / 1%) (+ 1% per 100 bonus AD) (+ 0.5% per 100 AP) of target's maximum health

ACTIVE: Shyvana surrounds herself in a wind storm, giving her decaying movement speed.

During this time, Shyvana's basic attacks deal a portion of their damage and on hit effects to surrounding enemies, and extend the duration of the storm by 1 second, which can occur up to 4 times for a total 4 seconds.

ATTACK/ON-HIT EFFECTIVENESS:
30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50%
BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED:
30 / 35 / 40 / 45 / 50% (+ 8% per 100 AP)
BONUS MOVEMENT SPEED DECAY:
4.5 / 5.25 / 6 / 6.75 / 7.5%

DRAGON FORM BONUS: During Fiery Winds Shyvana leaves a trail of flames behind her, dealing the same magic damage per tick and marking embers to enemies in the trail.

Additionally, Shyvana gains bonus attack speed during the storm.

BONUS ATTACK SPEED:
30 / 40 / 50% (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)

[Fireball]
COOLDOWN: 16 / 14 / 12 / 10 / 8

ACTIVE: Shyvana lobs a fireball in the target direction that explodes upon hitting an enemy champion, dealing magic damage to all enemies hit and creating a scorched field for 4 seconds. Enemies within the field are dealt additional magic damage every 0.5 seconds.

MAGIC DAMAGE:
30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+ 20% AD) (+ 50% AP)

MAGIC DAMAGE PER TICK:
15 / 30 / 45 / 60 / 75 (+ 10% AD) (+ 25% AP)

DRAGON FORM BONUS: 
The fireball deals increased magic damage and the size of the scorched field is doubled.

EMPOWERED MAGIC DAMAGE:
100 âˆ’ 160 (based on level) + 30 / 60 / 90 / 120 / 150 (+ 60% AD) (+ 80% AP)

[Dragon's Descent]
PASSIVE - FURY: Dragon's Descent requires 200 Fury to be cast. Shyvana generates Fury per second while alive and in HUMAN FORM and 2 Fury per basic attack on-hit in either form. Shyvana gains 200 Fury upon learning Dragon's Descent.

FURY GENERATION PER SECOND:
1 / 1.5 / 2
ACTIVE: Shyvana briefly channels then transforms into DRAGON FORM and takes to the skies to fly to the target location, scorching the earth below her dealing magic damage before landing at the end of her path.

MAGIC DAMAGE:
150 / 200 / 250 (+ 70% AP)
DRAGON FORM: Shyvana gains bonus health, bonus attack range, increased size, and access to Dragon Breath. Her abilities are also empowered to apply an additional effect. She maintains DRAGON FORM at a recurring cost of Fury, returning to Human Form once all Fury has been depleted.

BONUS HEALTH:
100 / 150 / 200 (+ 100% bonus AD) (+ 75% AP)
BONUS RANGE:
50 / 75 / 100
SIZE INCREASE:
0 / 8.5 / 16%

[Dragon Breath]
COST: 20 / 15 / 10 fury per second.
COOLDOWN: 5 / 2.5 / 0
ACTIIVE: Shyvana prepares for a brief moment, then channels to breathe fire in a cone in front of her for as long as she channels, draining fury per second and dealing magic and physical damage per tick to enemies, and applying on-hit effects at reduced effectiveness.

MAGIC DAMAGE:
20 / 35 / 50  (+ 20 / 25 / 30% AP) (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)

PHYSICAL DAMAGE:
20 / 35 / 50 (+ 30 / 40 / 50% AD) (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)

ON-HIT EFFECTIVENESS:
20 / 30 / 40% (based on the level of Dragon's Descent)
